INFO Master Fisher gives you Tunas (you fish your own lobbies/swordies) Clan system with clan chat, clan houses & clan territories Custom flags (US,Germany, etc) K/D ratio (killing the same person in a row does not count unless he/she is in gear or if he/she kills you) 1 account can be made every two hours. 15x exp in wild Pirates drop death runes (1 each) Men drops 50gp each Everyone can use SAY (20 seconds before you can use it again, however to minimize spam) Rares will be implemented once the server becomes active Already selected Admins (who helped me create this server) and mods.
